---
// Hero section with tagline and version
---

<section class="py-20 text-center">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
    <h2 data-test="hero-tagline" class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
      When <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">philosophy guides implementation</span>,<br>
      code becomes clear
    </h2>

    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      RootSpec is a specification methodology that creates self-validating,
      implementation-ready documentation through structured hierarchy and clear boundaries.
    </p>

    <div class="flex justify-center items-center space-x-6">
      <span data-test="version-badge" class="bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900 text-green-800 dark:text-green-200 px-4 py-2 rounded-full font-medium">
        v7.0.9
      </span>

      <a href="https://github.com/rootspec/rootspec" data-test="github-link" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        Explore GitHub →
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>